Class MainMenuState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nkoiv.mists.game.gamestate.MainMenuState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GameState

    public class MainMenuState
extends Object
implements GameState
    MainMenuState controls and manages the main menu. Because of the simplicity of the main menu, there is no separate class for it. Main menu is really only composed of UI-components, like buttons.
